1.create package.json with default values = npm init -y
2.install nodemon and add it to dev dependendies as devDependencies is that what use while developing tools = npm install nodemon --save-dev
3. create server.js file
4. setup package.json start to nodemon server.js to keep server listening to changes as you doing them. 
5.create server.js and start listening for calls, for that simply call http://localhost:3000/ and start looking for webbrowsers calls